{"tid":972013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蠢男酒後「挑釁」大象…慘遭象足踐踏慘死","createTime":"2019-01-07T05:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T14:48:20.000Z","uid":75969,"like":140,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"61a5fc86869efdc0b0d3adf1f4bb86bc479fff7c","tid":972013,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:39:37.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n斯里蘭卡一名41歲男子日前參加旅行團，到當地的雅拉國家公園參觀野生動物，沒想到途中男子酒後一時性起，突然接近一頭大象進行挑釁，結果大象看到後突然向前猛衝，直接將該名男子踩死，影片曝光後引起網路熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/06/1723054-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F06%2F1723054-XXL.jpg&h=43abd33b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲男子遭大象踩踏慘死。（圖／翻攝自Elephant's aquarium Corners YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，死者是斯里蘭卡當地居民，當時男子違規從車內離開，接近一頭野生的大象，甚至還向其挑釁，結果才會意外慘死在象足之下。一名雅拉國家公園的主管透露，男子事發前已經喝醉酒，可能因此才會挑釁大象。<br />\n<br />\n斯里蘭卡野生動物司司長尚達納（Chandana Sooriyabandara）指出，法律規定民眾不得在入園期間從車上離開、閒晃，男子的行徑實屬違法，同時也提醒民眾，未來任何人做出類似行為都將受到法律制裁。（編輯：陳又瑞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m6_fWi8m_Ag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm6_fWi8m_Ag&d=CLvBSNi7HEDZp085ZmrW7p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=56afd747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m6_fWi8m_Ag</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=481212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D481212&d=CLvBSNi7HEDZp085ZmrW7p4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=07162b09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D481212&h=595221d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=481212</a>"},{"pid":"50a9e08b4c6412093302654ffd2de49cd10b5a4c","tid":972013,"uid":157197,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"死到好撚7"},{"pid":"79d6c4be42f3623eb5bd1cf63584e9b271d8923b","tid":972013,"uid":63909,"like"